org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.params.xml.ns.yang.flowguard.rev170505

Interface Rule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AddRuleInput, RuleRegistryEntry

    public interface Rule
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module flowguard 

     grouping rule {
     leaf name {
         type string;
     }
     leaf node {
         type string;
     }
     leaf sourceMacAddress {
         type string;
     }
     leaf destinationMacAddress {
         type string;
     }
     leaf sourceIpAddress {
         type string;
     }
     leaf destinationIpAddress {
         type string;
     }
     leaf sourcePort {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf destinationPort {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf protocol {
         type enumeration;
     }
     leaf action {
         type enumeration;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is flowguard/rule
